      "content": "i feel like i’m just staring at a blank wall all day. the colors are gone. the part of me that actually *sees* things... it's just dead. i look in the mirror and there's nothing behind my eyes. just an empty house with the lights turned off. i don't even know why i'm still walking around if there's nothing left inside me to drive it.",
