    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "sparks dont really work when the furnace is gone. it's not just being bored or sad. it feels like the person who used to live here moved out a long time ago and left the lights off. i'm just... a shell. a biological machine that keeps moving because it has to, but there is no \"me\" anymore. how do you fix something that's just an empty container?",
